Project: Plogger YouTube
Author: Tom Medhurst <tom.medhurst@gmail.com>
Decription: Allows you to post YouTube videos (and possibly other video providers) into Plogger.

Installation

1. Overwrite the picture.php file in your theme (plog-content/themes/your_theme/) with the one attached.
2. Go to YouTube and save a copy of the thumbnail which represents your video
3. Upload the thumbail, and in the description field enter "YouTube:" followed by the YouTube code for the video
4. That's it!

For a more in-depth tutorial (with screenshots!) see http://www.tommed.co.uk/?p=16

Enjoy! ;)
